locations: Australia Zoo, Sunshine Coast, Queensland, Australia
imdb.plot outline: Robert Irwin teams up with Isabel Yamazaki to reveal how science has made mankind a true student of Mother Nature. In each episode, Robert and Isabel explore nature's amazing solutions for problems in the wild and reveal how humans use these blueprints to make the world greener, safer, more efficient and more fun for future generations.
